Sample Input

STDIN           Function
-----           --------
6               arr[] size n = 6
-4 3 -9 0 4 1   arr = [-4, 3, -9, 0, 4, 1]
Sample Output

0.500000
0.333333
0.166667

There are 3 positive numbers,  2 negative numbers, and 1 zero in the array.
positiv numbers = 3/6 = 0,500000
neqative numbers = 2/6= 0,333333
zero numbers = 1/6=0,16667